sentences.english: It was the site of a British victory over the Saxons in571. Population, 74, 500.
sentences.chinese: 它是571年大不列顛人打敗撒克遜人的遺址。

sentences.english: England or Great Britain. Often used poetically.
sentences.chinese: 阿爾比恩英格蘭或大不列顛。

sentences.english: Hadrian's Wall is built across Britannia to keep out the barbarians .
sentences.chinese: 橫貫大不列顛的哈德連長城被修築用來防禦野蠻人。

sentences.english: It was the site of a British victory over the Saxons in 57. Population, 74,500.

sentences.english: Rome's military invasion of Great Britain, Scottish pipers introduced.
sentences.chinese: 羅馬軍隊入侵大不列顛的時候，風笛傳入蘇格蘭。

sentences.english: Ben Nevis (1343m) the highest mountain in Britain is located in Scotland.
sentences.chinese: 位於蘇格蘭的本尼威斯山是大不列顛的最高山。

sentences.english: Great Britain has only two sleeper trains.
sentences.chinese: 大不列顛只有兩條臥鋪列車線路，都是快客。

sentences.english: The United Kingdom consists of Great Britain and Northern Island.
sentences.chinese: 聯合王國是由大不列顛及北愛爾蘭組成。

sentences.english: The United Kingdom consists of Great Britain and the Northern Ireland.
sentences.chinese: 聯合王國是由大不列顛和北愛爾蘭所組成。

sentences.english: Many of London's streets help narrate British history.
sentences.chinese: 許多倫敦的街道都在敷陳着大不列顛的歷史。

sentences.english: The coronation of King George I of Great Britain and Ireland took place.
sentences.chinese: 大不列顛和愛爾蘭聯合王國國王喬治一世加冕。

sentences.english: Triumph, my Britain, thou hast one to show.
sentences.chinese: 歡樂吧，我的大不列顛，你有一個人向世人展現。

sentences.english: Five variations for piano on "Rule Britannia".
sentences.chinese: 五對“第大不列顛”鋼琴變奏曲。

sentences.english: Many of The Queen's official tours were undertaken on the Royal Yacht Britannia.
sentences.chinese: 女王多次出訪均乘坐皇家遊艇“大不列顛號”。

sentences.english: So there you go. "Appropriate and proportionate", as is the British way.
sentences.chinese: 隨你便了，“合理適度”又是大不列顛的老一套了。

sentences.english: You've got Britain which is those same things.
sentences.chinese: 你聽到的大不列顛帝國也是一樣。
